title: Startup Grind LA
description: Interview at Startup Grind Los Angeles on July 21st, 2015 at Expert Dojo's 3rd story deck on 3rd Street Promenade in front of a sold out crowd. Gary discusses his childhood, early career, angel investing, hiring & firing, owning & playing for the Jets, immortality, and much more. Gary also takes questions from the audience. The interview is conducted by Startup Grind LA Director Joe Famalette.
